<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <base href="../" />
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="assets/favicon.ico" />
  <!-- Font Awesome icons (free version)-->
  <script src="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v6.4.2/js/all.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:400,700" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto+Slab:400,100,300,700" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
  <!-- Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)-->
  <link href="css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <title>About - Red & Blue Appliances Service</title>
</head>

<body id="page-top">
  <!-- Navigation-->
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark fixed-top" id="mainNav">
    <div class="container">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="/"><img src="assets/img/navbar-logo.png" alt="Red & Blue Appliances Service" /></a>
      <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarResponsive" aria-controls="navbarResponsive" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
        Menu
        <i class="fas fa-bars ms-1"></i>
      </button>
      <div class="logo-text" style="color: white;">Red & Blue Appliances Service</div>
      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarResponsive">
        <ul class="navbar-nav text-uppercase ms-auto py-1 py-lg-0">
          <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li class="nav-item dropdown">
            <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="/services" id="servicesDropdown" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">Services</a>
            <div class="dropdown-menu bg-red" aria-labelledby="servicesDropdown">
              <% services = [
              [ 'refrigerator', 'Refrigerator' ],
              [ 'hood', 'Hood' ],
              [ 'dishwasher', 'Dishwasher' ],
              [ 'stoves', 'Stoves' ],
              [ 'microwave', 'Microwave' ],
              [ 'ice_machine', 'Ice Machine' ],
              [ 'washer_dryer', 'Washer & Dryer' ],
              [ 'wall_oven', 'Wall Oven' ]
            ] %>
              <% services.forEach((service) => { %>
                <a class="dropdown-item text-white" href="/services/<%= service[0]%>"><%= service[1]%></a>
              <%})%>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/aboutus">About Us</a></li>
          <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Masthead-->
  <header class="masthead" style="padding: 10rem 2rem; background-image: url('./assets/img/header-bg-about.png');">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="masthead-heading text-white" style="padding-top: 6rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">About Us</div>
      <div class="masthead-subheading text-white" style="font-size: x-large;">Behind the Tools, Beyond the Services: Unveiling Our Appliance Repair Journey</div>
    </div>
  </header>
  
  <!-- Locations -->
  <section class="page-section" style="padding: 4rem 0;">
    <div class="container px-0">
      <h6 class="text-blue" style="font-weight: 700; padding-bottom: 3rem;"><center>Welcome to Red & Blue Appliances Service, your trusted partner for all your appliance repair needs. At Red & Blue, we take pride in our commitment to excellence, customer satisfaction, and the mastery of our craft.</center></h6>

        <h3>Who We Are</h2>
        <h6 style="font-weight: 400; padding-bottom: 3rem">Founded in [Year], Red & Blue Appliances Service is a family-owned and operated business with a passion for delivering top-notch appliance repair solutions. We understand the integral role that household appliances play in your daily life, and that's why we're dedicated to keeping them in optimal working condition.</h6>

        <h3>Our Mission</h2>
        <h6 style="font-weight: 400; padding-bottom: 3rem">Our mission is simple: to provide reliable, efficient, and affordable appliance repair services that exceed your expectations. We believe in the power of a well-maintained appliance to make your life easier, and we're here to ensure your appliances perform at their best.</h6>

        <h3>Our Team</h2>
        <h6 style="font-weight: 400; padding-bottom: 3rem">Our team is composed of highly skilled technicians who are experts in their field. They undergo rigorous training and stay updated with the latest industry trends and technologies to serve you better. We pride ourselves on our professionalism, punctuality, and friendly demeanor.</h6>

        <h3>What Sets Us Apart</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Prompt Service:</strong> We understand the urgency of appliance issues, which is why we strive to provide quick and efficient service. When you need us, we're just a call away.</li>
            <li><strong>Affordable Rates:</strong> We believe that quality appliance repair shouldn't break the bank. Our competitive pricing ensures that you get the best value for your money.</li>
            <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> We believe in transparent communication. Before any repair, we provide a detailed estimate, so you know what to expect.</li>
            <li><strong>Customer-Centric Approach:</strong> Your satisfaction is our top priority. We're committed to not just meeting but exceeding your expectations.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <center><img src="./assets/img/navbar-logo.png" width="100%" height="100%" style="max-width: 400px; margin: 4rem;"/></center>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer-->
  <footer class="footer py-4 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-lg-4 text-lg-start">Copyright &copy; Red & Blue Appliances Service LLC 2023</div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 my-3 my-lg-0">
          <a class="btn btn-dark btn-social mx-2" href="#!" aria-label="Twitter"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
          <a class="btn btn-dark btn-social mx-2" href="#!" aria-label="Facebook"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
          <a class="btn btn-dark btn-social mx-2" href="#!" aria-label="LinkedIn"><i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i></a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 text-lg-end">
          <a class="link-dark text-decoration-none me-3" href="#!">Privacy Policy</a>
          <a class="link-dark text-decoration-none" href="#!">Terms of Use</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center text-blue" style="padding-top: 2rem; font-weight: 900;">RED AND BLUE APPLIANCES SERVICE LLC</div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="js/scripts.js"></script>
  <div class="sticky-button fa-fade">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-truck fa-lg" style="color: #ffffff; padding-right: 8px; padding-left: 8px;"></i>
    <a href="/contact">Request a Service</a>
  </div>
</body>

</html>